					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I saw TL333s's comment and immediately clicked the article. Charming and not too long; just my kind of read.</p> <p>I remember George from one of Sir David Attenborough's documentaries.</p> <blockquote> <p>On the morning of 6/24/2012, &quot;Lonesome George&quot;, the last non-anomalous Abingdon Island tortoise, died. The population of SCP-3759 organized into a circular arrangement, and in the center of the circle, a new instance of SCP-3759 manifested.</p> </blockquote> <p>TAKE MY UPVOTE.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
